* Phrasal Verbs
* Academic Vocabulary
* Mixed Challenge

---

# Academy Progression

Every Academy contains six mastery levels.

Only the first level is unlocked initially.

The remaining levels unlock as the previous level is completed.

```
Foundation
    ↓
Explorer
    ↓
Practitioner
    ↓
Scholar
    ↓
Master
    ↓
Legend
```

Each level contains its own collection of puzzles.

Vocabulary difficulty increases naturally from one level to the next.

---

# Replay System

Completed levels remain permanently unlocked.

Players may replay any completed level whenever they wish.

Replaying levels allows players to:

* Improve accuracy
* Earn additional coins
* Improve completion statistics
* Practice difficult vocabulary

---

