# Save System

Everything is stored locally.

There is:

* No account
* No login
* No email
* No password
* No cloud save
* No database
* No monthly server costs

The game works completely offline.

If the app is deleted or app data is cleared, progress is lost. Purchased non-consumable items can be restored through **Restore Purchases**.

